      <h1>About Virtual Coach AI</h1>
      <p><strong>Virtual Coach AI</strong> brings tour-level coaching to everyday golfers with AI-powered swing analysis, mental game scoring, and personalized practice plans.</p>
    </header>

    <p>Built by PGA professional <strong>Jim Hartnett</strong> with modern AI, the platform makes elite performance accessible, understandable, and actionable—regardless of location or skill level.</p>

    <p>Jim’s experience spans premier facilities like Kapalua (Maui), Sahalee (WA), and PGA West (CA), plus time with top instructors like Jim McLean. That depth is now fused with AI to guide improvement swing by swing.</p>

    <p>Core focus: deliver truly personalized instruction at scale. Virtual Coach AI combines biomechanics insights, instant feedback tools, and an easy workflow so you can learn faster and smarter.</p>

    <p><strong>What’s next:</strong> real-time motion tracking, 3D comparisons, a full Mental IQ system, and adaptive practice plans that evolve with your progress.</p>

    <p>Whether you’re chasing your first birdie or dialing in your scoring game potential, Virtual Coach AI keeps you out of the dark and on a plan. Welcome to the future of golf improvement.</p>
